create transaction

1. should not be able to use any other transaction type than 'credit' or 'debit'
2. should not be able to create a transaction on other's category
3. should not be able to create transaction on other's account
4. should not be able to create transaction without authorization
5. title can't be empty
6. amount cant' be empty
7. should be able to create without category
8. should be able to create without account
9. should be able to create without description
10. should be able to create without transaction type (default should be taken)
11. should be able to create without datetime
